{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Navigate Act 1 of a world that reacts to your paint.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293560/extras/PaintingGif.gif?t=1737241904\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore two early zones of the game, change the state of puzzles, and repair things that have been broken to progress.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Find unique abilities and use crystals to upgrade your abilities.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293560/extras/AbilitiesGif.gif?t=1737241904\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you explore you will discover powerful relics. Crystals you find can be channeled to unlock these abilities and upgrade them further so that you can survive and affect the dangerous landscape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Get help from this world's denizens.<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293560/extras/DialogueGif.gif?t=1737241904\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Help various characters with quests, trade with them, and get to know them to unlock important information and powerful upgrades.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Find all available relics and fully explore the two maps.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293560/extras/Vatii.gif?t=1737241904\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Complete each of the 2 areas to complete the demo. Re-explore past areas to unlock every ability and upgrade and meet all of the characters.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293560/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737241904","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293560/page.bg.jpg?t=1737241904","capsule_image":"https://sha